				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Having fun with my BoH....<a name="10807"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 25 03 12:07 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Yesterday my guild leader asked me to meet up with her bazaar bot as she had something for me, so I hot tailed (litterally tailed, I'm a Vah Shir<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /> it to the bazaar where I was presented with a Breath of Harmony.  I was extremely happy at this and then it hit me... I suck at mixing clickies into twists....
<br />

<br />
It was a quiet day so I decided to start messing about with this to try and get the twisting down when it hit me.  The effect on the BoH is an instant cast clicky...  Remembering when I was working on my skills: Sense Traps, Disarm Traps and Sense Heading I quickly linked the BoH to hot button number 0 and then setup the down arrow key as an alternate key for this button.  So now my twist goes:
<br />

<br />
1 1, down arrow, 2 2, 3 3, down arrow, 4 4
<br />

<br />
Beautiful, five songs twisting muwahahahaa</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
